title: Styles P Versus Chad Ochocinco Johnson | Is Kanye vs Drake Too Messy For Hip-Hop
description:
IAA Miami Season 3: Episode 2

Brandon Marshall, Chad Ochocinco Johnson, Channing Crowder, and Fred Taylor sit down with rapper, Styles P as he drops gems on growth and health. Styles reflects on his career as a member of The Lox and gives us his take on the current state of hip-hop. Ochocinco takes things to the next level when he challenges Styles P to a must see freestyle battle.
